.demo-description
  %p
    This example demonstrates dynamic resizing of a grid. It is known that the width of grid is
    sum of the width of the columns. We can overwrite this by setting the grid width. In this
    case the column width are scaled to the new width. With setting the height to 100% we can
    scale the height of the grid. Try to go on next page.
/ End demo-description
